" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Company Dashboard</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/mycompany-dashboard.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters My Company dashboard"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Company Dashboard</h4> <p>The My Company dashboard provides managers a high level view into all activities of the company with ticket and task statistics with drill down capability. Also included is a Work Class Breakdown chart, invaluable for resource management, displaying predicted levels of project, support and operational work compared to current actual, last month actual and two months prior actual.</p></div></div><span id="mcSD"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#srvdesk"><img src="img/mycompany-servicedesk-dashboard.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters my company service desk dashboard" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="srvdesk" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="srvdesk" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Company Service Desk Dashboard</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/mycompany-servicedesk-dashboard.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters my company service desk dashboard"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Company Service Desk Dashboard</h4> <p>The Service Desk Dashboard provides graphical evidence of work in progress and completed including: ticket statistics, top 5 in ticket volume by products, top five in ticket volume by location, top five in ticket volume by type, problem statistics, and ticket trends over the past three months. All graphs are click-able with drill down capability. </p></div></div><span id="mcQueues"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#mcqueues"><img src="img/mycompany-queue-dashboard.png" alt="My Company Service Desk Dashboard" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="mcqueues" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="mcqueues" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Company Queues Dashboard</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/mycompany-queue-dashboard.png" style="width:100%" alt="My Company Service Desk Dashboard"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Company Queues Dashboard</h4> <p>The Queues Dashboard provides list of queues with customizable grid controls, advanced search capability and the ability to review and manage unlimited queues. Drill down into any queue and subsequent ticket, manage teams, and run reports. </p></div></div><span id="mcProjects"></span> <div class="media panel"> <a class="pull-right media-object" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#mcproj"><img src="img/mycompany-project-dashboard.png" alt="TeamHeadquarters project time sheet management" width="300" height="139"></a> <div class="modal fade" id="mcproj" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="mcproj" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button> <h4>My Company Projects Dashboard</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <img src="img/mycompany-project-dashboard.png" style="width:100%" alt="TeamHeadquarters my teams time sheet"> </div></div></div></div><div class="media-body"> <h4 class="media-heading" >My Company Projects Dashboard</h4> <p>The Projects Dashboard delivers a list of projects with customizable grid controls, advanced